title: Pink Floyd - Rhapsody In Pink [Vinyl Rip]
description:
Nice vinyl rip (including real genuine surface noise! - though not much!!!) ripped directly from vinyl source [played on Michel Gyrodec] to uncompressed audio.

This is the full version of the Rhapsody In Pink LP which is taken from various BBC sessions. The quality is superb, and in my opinion, even surpasses some of the officially released versions! Enjoy!
